{"tid":1836753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"繼武漢後再封第2城！湖北黃岡市午夜起也圍城","createTime":"2020-01-23T10:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T16:38:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f357ea719d7758de0c594a4944f47e308eba35ca","tid":1836753,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T10:18:03.000Z","msg":"在距離湖北武漢一個多小時車程的黃岡市，星期五午夜起停運市內公共交通及長途客運，並會暫時關閉城鐵站及火車站離開黃岡的通道；要求居民無特殊原因不要離開市區。<br />\n<br />\n所有進出黃岡的道路出入口，會對所有往來的車輛及人員進行疫情排查，進出人員要檢測體溫，交通工具搭載的動物要檢查。市內所有影劇院、網吧和室內公共文化、旅遊及娛樂場所暫停營業；黃州區中心市場休市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200123/ZSJ6CSV3AO656P32TGWRAZBBKQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200123%2FZSJ6CSV3AO656P32TGWRAZBBKQ%2F&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=2fa997ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200123%2FZSJ6CSV3AO656P32TGWRAZBBKQ%2F&h=85b0158a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200123/ZSJ6CSV3AO656P32TGWRAZBBKQ/</a>"},{"pid":"9bbbad55630af0c26403c266d4daa4f23c3242f0","tid":1836753,"uid":85427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T10:19:27.000Z","msg":"封城開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e11eca0511d5748ffe6fd9f39479f87f8037d23","tid":1836753,"uid":22888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T10:20:51.000Z","msg":"香港繼續輸入武漢人來港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdd734a8d4ae947b8628d59f516538a5deb905e","tid":1836753,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T10:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/23/182053_123d1e4e75deea3722a8350565fecec0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservic